Class JarGenrule

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.AbstractBuildRule

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasOutputName, HasDeclaredAndExtraDeps, SupportsInputBasedRuleKey, BuildRule, BinaryBuildRule, Comparable<BuildRule>

    public class JarGenrule
extends Genrule
implements BinaryBuildRule
    A rule similar to Genrule except specialized to produce a jar.

    The produced jar behaves similarly to a jar produced by java_binary, which means it can be executed by buck run or using the $(exe ) macro.
